  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the effect of General versus Local Anaesthesia on
      muscle and cerebral oxygenation under EVAR-treatment in a prospective unblinded randomised
      controlled trail.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
